Subject: [PATCH v2 4/8] ftrace: Add DYNAMIC_FTRACE_WITH_CALL_OPS
Date:   Fri, 13 Jan 2023 18:03:51 +0000
Message-Id: <20230113180355.2930042-5-mark.rutland@arm.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.30.2
In-Reply-To: <20230113180355.2930042-1-mark.rutland@arm.com>
